## Completeness Score

Each listing should have a completeness score.

Suggested weighting:

- Basic details: 20%
- Technical details: 25%
- Photos: 25%
- Documents: 20%
- Sale setup: 10%

Show missing required items explicitly.

Example:

ZS-ABC Cessna 172N
Draft
Completeness: 72%
Missing:
- Engine logbook summary
- Cockpit powered-on photo
- Asking price

